trans-unit.source: Represents an element in a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Representa um elemento em uma classe <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class represents the \<schemeSettings> element under the Uri section within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> classe representa o \<schemeSettings > elemento na seção de Uri dentro de um arquivo de configuração.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> class represents an instance of an element in the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> classe representa uma instância de um elemento de <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> classe.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> class and the \<schemeSettings> section in a configuration file looks generic, implying that an application can specify any <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for any scheme.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElementCollection> classe e o \<schemeSettings > seção em um arquivo de configuração é genérica, indicando que um aplicativo pode especificar qualquer <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> valor de enumeração de qualquer esquema.

trans-unit.source: In fact, only the <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType> flag for HTTP and HTTPS schemes are supported.
trans-unit.target: Na verdade, somente o <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions.DontUnescapePathDotsAndSlashes?displayProperty=nameWithType> sinalizador para esquemas HTTP e HTTPS são aceitos.
Todas as outras configurações são ignoradas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the GenericUriParserOptions entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor da entrada GenericUriParserOptions de uma instância <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> propriedade retorna um <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> valor de enumeração para a <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instância.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the Name entry from a <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor da entrada Nome de uma instância <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement" />.

trans-unit.source: The protocol used by this schema setting.
trans-unit.target: O protocolo usado por essa configuração de esquema.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> property returns a <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> enumeration value for the <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instance.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> propriedade retorna um <xref:System.GenericUriParserOptions?displayProperty=nameWithType> valor de enumeração para a <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement> instância.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> element is currently restricted to HTPP and HTTPS.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.SchemeSettingElement.GenericUriParserOptions%2A> elemento está restrito atualmente HTPP e HTTPS.
